道精神」主席Mark Brooks亦有類似的看法，質疑如果犯人是男性，裁決或會大大不同：「如果案中的性別倒轉，我們會預望任何犯此犯罪行為的男人，都被關進入監獄中」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實班人係咪打簡體出稿</blockquote><br />\n支那寫稿佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ab8910906cef0eb6f56a33d6b60d36821e177d","tid":416921,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efa76fd1d63e66f59157f7ae0a27d9534480efab","tid":416921,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"女權入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04573e8f807ab81c4b6ee73380572b2ad9fb8e75","tid":416921,"uid":16034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇相都知無罪啦，冇問題</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係好想睇 如果有日有條正菜黎殺你全家 係咪真係無問題"},{"pid":"7653dccd439dcf739dae05a8edda2b79dce9dad0","tid":416921,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:17:04.000Z","msg":"割傷姐<br />\n而且係用家底同背景求情求到唔使坐<br />\n只能話家底太強<br />\n佢割得唔夠犀利"},{"pid":"a07194c7eaf060a19963a5886a837343615e3b18","tid":416921,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:26:20.000Z","msg":"之前已經有人開過post"},{"pid":"2bc7668913362917dd36072c01ffeb22a3984271","tid":416921,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:28:48.000Z","msg":"男人老狗比人幾下就報驚<br />\n正垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2b740180c3c55f598c6b0c742606ed3890eab1","tid":416921,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:29:47.000Z","msg":"我認同"},{"pid":"f3b087c8b24c83f9dbaacd73f70c4aad2a86bbf1","tid":416921,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:47:51.000Z","msg":"幫法官含過撚？"},{"pid":"712052d2edcc313c81a7494cb4c8d4e969cc7198","tid":416921,"uid":247